      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''We are going for work, but always in tension. Anytime, shelling or bombing comes from all directions. We are frightened, but what are we to do?''</p>
        <p>SAROJINI SRI SOMASEGARAM of Jaffna, on the ethnic conflict in Sri Lanka. [A6]</p>
